# 🔐 Wazuh SOC Lab

## 📌 Project Overview

This project demonstrates a complete SOC (Security Operations Center) lab using Wazuh SIEM.

## 🧱 Architecture

* Wazuh Server (Ubuntu 22.04)
* Windows 10 Client (Agent)
* Web Dashboard (HTTPS)

## ⚙️ Setup

* Installed Wazuh all-in-one (Indexer + Manager + Dashboard)
* Connected Windows agent
* Enabled Windows auditing (auditpol)

## 🧪 Tests Performed

### 1. Failed Login Detection

* Simulated failed login attempts
* Detected Event ID 4625 in Wazuh

### 2. Privilege Escalation Detection

* Detected "Failed attempt to perform a privileged operation"

### 3. Command Execution

* Executed commands via PowerShell / CMD
* Observed logs in Wazuh dashboard

## 📊 Results

* Real-time monitoring working
* Alerts generated successfully
* SOC environment fully functional

